data.description: Don't miss this amazing all brick home in the Wells Forest Subdivision! You'll love the quietness of the small neighborhood but the convenience to everything you need. Upon entering the foyer you'll notice the amazing hardwood floors that lead to a very open area for living, dining and cooking. The coziness of the fireplace can be enjoyed from all 3 rooms. To the right you'll love the privacy of the master suite which has a large walk in closet, new carpet, a separate shower and a enjoyable garden tub. On the other side of the home you'll find 2 more bedrooms with a shared full bath in between. The laundry room, which is off of the garage, has tons of cabinet space as well as a convenient utility sink. There are many utility, linen and coat closets throughout. Upstairs is an enormous FROG that has a large closet for the 4th bedroom. Upstairs you'll also find the convenience of a 1/2 bath. Exiting the dining room area you'll enter a spacious screened in porch where you'll enjoy sitting or reading in full privacy. The back yard is fully private due to the brick fencing. Iron exit gates are on both sides of the backyard, with paved sidewalks to the front. New water heater, garage door opener & front storm door!  Check this one out before it's gone, private and quiet yet minutes to the Universities,  Walmart, Lowes, Groceries, gas and restaurants! This is a great location within an hour of Columbia or Charleston!
